modName: Scouter Corset by NEO Conversion to UNPB BBP BBPx TBBP
summary:
Conversion of Scouter Corset by NEO to UNPB UNPB-BBP UNPB-BBPx bodies. With working weight slider

Experimental TBBP release included
descriptionHtml:
Conversion of Scouter Corset by NEO to UNPB UNPB-BBP UNPB-BBPx bodies. With working weight slider

Needs original UNP mod installed first [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/18912] Scouter Corset by NEO Meister aka Neovinci[/url]

This conversion was done by request of Zonzai, author of [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/1040/]The Art of Magicka[/url]
for a mod that is/was being worked on.

BBP version require
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/20227]UNPB Body Main Page[/url]

Experimental TBBP release ------ If you don't know about TBBP, don't use this.

Special thanks to Neo for the creation and permission to release this conversion.
